com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.backend
Class TestGenerator

java.lang.Object
  com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.backend.TestGenerator

public class TestGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

This singleton represents the principal API of KeYTestGen2. It supports the following modes of operation:

  • Generate a test suite only for a subset case methods in a class.
  • Generate a test suite for all methods in a class, with the option of including protected, private and methods inherited from java.lang.Object.
  • Generate a test suite only for a single IExecutionNode.
For any of the options above the user can supply an implementation of IFrameworkConverter in order to specify in what format the resulting test suite(s) should be returned. If none is supplied (i.e. if the parameter is null), then KeYTestGen2 will use its internal XML format by default.

For any of the options above, the user has the option deciding the level of code coverage to be provided, by supplying an instance of ICodeCoverageParser. By default. Statement Coverage should be targeted.

public java.util.List<ITestSuite> generateTestSuite(java.lang.String source,
                                                    ICodeCoverageParser coverage,
                                                    IFrameworkConverter converter,
                                                    boolean includePublic,
                                                    boolean includeProtected,
                                                    boolean includePrivate,
                                                    boolean includeNative)
                                             throws TestGeneratorException
Parameters:
source - path to the Java source file.
coverage - code coverage critera to be satisfied by the generated test cases. May be null, in which case a default statement coverage is used. See ICodeCoverageParser.
converter - converter to turn the output of KTG into code for a given testing framework. See IFrameworkConverter.
includePublic - set to true to generate test cases for all public methods.
includeProtected - set to true to generate test cases for all protected methods.
includePrivate - set to true to generate test cases for all private methods.
includeNative - set to true to generate test cases also for methods inherited from java.lang.Object.
Returns:
a test suite for the target class, in the specified test framework.
Throws:
TestGeneratorException - in the event that something went wrong in the process of test case generation.
